Return to the House of 1,000 Doors to save mankind from annihilation.
Giant snakes have burst out of the Earth and are wreaking destruction
across every continent. Your mission: travel back in time to four
different epochs to gather the elements needed to activate a machine
that can destroy the ancient beasts.
